summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Plat 226W, page 15, of the official Zoning Map of The City of Seattle (Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property in the Southwest Quarter of Section 29, Township 26 North, Range 4 East, W.M., from RS 7200 to RM 800 (Petition of Ann Segale, C.F. 284504, X-77-018).
